g.text: The Experimental Systems & Technology Lab (ESTL) is a leading software development team in Singapores Ministry of Education. Our engineers build cutting-edge software to simplify the responsibilities of teachers and administrative staff. Our products include School Cockpit Mobile (SC Mobile), School Timetabling Application (STA), School Cockpit 2.0 and Surveys.
WHAT DO WE DO AS EDUCATION OFFICERS IN ESTL?

Education Officers (EOs) are champions of the users. We know the ground best, and have utmost empathy for all our teachers. Together with our software engineers, we design solutions to help schools with their administrative tasks.The EOs in ESTL ensure that the right products are built, while the engineers ensure the products are built right.
